text: Castets et Castillon is a commune. It is found in the region Nouvelle- Aquitaine in the Gironde department in the southwest of France. The municipality was created on 1 January 2017 and consists of the former communes of Castets-en-Dorthe (the seat) and Castillon-de-Castets.Arrêté préfectoral 1 August 2016 == References == Category:2017 establishments in France Category:Communes in Gironde
title: Castets et Castillon
